WEBVTT

00:00.163 --> 00:04.185
When he rescued us at the Forks, I swear the bullets refused to touch him.

00:05.003 --> 00:06.651
At Princeton, our lines failed,...

00:06.977 --> 00:10.857
...but he rode into a thousand deaths and willed victory.

00:11.794 --> 00:14.715
We were doomed at Monmouth until he led us on that charge.

00:14.918 --> 00:16.993
That forever changed the war!

00:17.336 --> 00:18.090
Hear, Hear!

00:18.201 --> 00:22.791
Before he was president, he was America's first action hero.

00:22.963 --> 00:25.094
Washington the Warrior.

00:25.343 --> 00:29.287
Memorial Day, as only the History Channel can bring you.

